<br>
57-59 spells you should spend a day in Trak's Lair slaying juggs.<br>
60 spells are pretty much boss mob only, Chardok prince, king, queen, Tolapumji, Sebilite Protector etc...<br>
<br>
I think dragons are the fastest and easiest way to get spells if your guild can manage it.<br>
I've done 4 dragons in the past couple weeks and have seen: 2x Spirit of Oak, 2x Banishment, Legacy of the Thorn, and Protection of the Glades.<br>
<br>
Avendel<br>
